Metadata.Title: ELSA-2007-1176:  Important: autofs security update  (IMPORTANT)
Metadata.Description:
[5.0.1-0.rc2.55.el5.2]
 - Bug 426219: CVE-2007-6285 autofs default doesn't set nodev in /net 
 [rhel-5.1.z]

 specified.
 - Related: rhbz#426219
